    while (scanner.hasNextLine()) {
        String line = scanner.nextLine();
        sum += Integer.parseInt(line);
    }

Or use `Files` for a one liner:

    int sum = Files.lines(Paths.get(&quot;E:/Java_Examples/data.txt&quot;))
